title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Paper & Paperboard & Related Articles
description: Imports Intra Eu - Paper & Paperboard & Related Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 463.14 GBP Million in September from 491.02 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Paper & Paperboard & Related Ar in the United Kingdom averaged 841.91 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 85253.80 GBP Million in March of 2015 and a record low of 129.50 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Paper & Paperboard & Relate.
